      ],
      "name": "section-help-text",
      "settings": {
        "title": "Why the right fit matters so much",
        "description": "<p class=\"section-help-text__text\">You wouldn’t buy them boots two sizes too big — gloves are no different.</p>\n<p class=\"section-help-text__text\">Poorly sized gloves affect:</p>\n<div class=\"section-help-text__items\">\n<div class=\"section-help-text__image img\">\n<div class=\"section-help-text__item\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/DSC08614.jpg?v=1749043352\" alt=\"\">\n<p class=\"section-help-text__desc\">Handling – The ball slips or feels “off”</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section-help-text__item\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/IMG_1965.jpg?v=1749043353\" alt=\"\">\n<p class=\"section-help-text__desc\">Confidence – They don’t trust their hands</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section-help-text__item\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/IMG_2398.png?v=1749043353\" alt=\"\">\n<p class=\"section-help-text__desc\">Durability – Oversized gloves wear down faster</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section-help-text__item\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/IMG_2522.jpg?v=1749043353\" alt=\"\">\n<p class=\"section-help-text__desc\">Technique – Bad habits creep in early</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"section-help-text__text\">And no — they shouldn’t “grow into them.” That only slows their progress.</p>"
      }
    },
